; Coverage test for xact.cc line 719
; Tests the verify() function with virtual postings that don't must_balance.
; An auto transaction adds a virtual posting (Memo:Taxed) plus two balancing
; real postings (Assets:Tax debit and Expenses:Tax credit).
; verify() must skip the virtual posting in its balance check.

= /Expenses:Food/
    Assets:Tax                   0.10
    Expenses:Tax                -0.10
    (Memo:Taxed)                -1.0

2024/01/01 Groceries
    Expenses:Food              $50.00
    Assets:Cash

test bal
             $-45.00  Assets
             $-50.00    Cash
               $5.00    Tax
              $45.00  Expenses
              $50.00    Food
              $-5.00    Tax
             $-50.00  Memo:Taxed
--------------------
             $-50.00
end test
